divs: Sighting DetailsDate of sighting-12-06-01 time 6:35pm.Place Palm Coast, Flagler Co. Fl. Jim wassitting on back deck when an object I first thought was a star was moving fromSE to NW.I went inside to get binoculars and told Jennifer to come out quick.Itracked the object which was starlike in appearance and I thought could be thespace station,or a satellite.The light was white and appeared to be selfgenerated. The object tracked straight overhead before disappearing to the NW.Atthe same time I was tracking object#1,Jennifer observed a similar objecttracking east ;she then observed three additional similar objects travelingdirectly behind the first object she observed.The three objects appeared to belined up diagonally following the first object she observed all in an easterlydirection.We both then observed a similar object tracking from north to south.Weboth then observed a similar object tracking se to nw.I also observed a similarobject moving fromn to s with only binoculars;I couldt pick it up with the nakedeye and lost it when I tried again with binos.
